		{"id":"634002c58101722a","type":"text","text":"修了最初有 bug：context_to_channels.weight 和 gate.weight 都初始化为 0，导致 phase_context 支路死掉。后来改成：\n\nnn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.context_to_channels.weight)\n\nnn.init.zeros_(self.context_to_channels.bias)\n\nnn.init.xavier_uniform_(self.gate.weight, gain=0.1)\n\nself.gate.bias.fill_(_initial_logit(0.7))\n\nRaw checkpoint 里 phase 支路现在已非零：\n\nmemory_gate.context_to_channels.weight nonzero = 1024/1024\n\nresidual_gate.context_to_channels.weight nonzero = 1024/1024\n\n但指标提升很小，说明相位支路虽然活了，贡献不明显。主要性能提升仍来自 门控式记忆筛选 + MST 输出残差稳定，而不是 phase_context 本身。","x":29,"y":2120,"width":451,"height":560},
		{"id":"cafcf7e1ec201961","type":"text","text":"RMSE=0.8400","x":620,"y":2395,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"26a0512ad8c45740","type":"text","text":"PhaseGatedMST Raw\n RMSE 0.8411","x":129,"y":1920,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"33d776fba813566e","type":"text","text":"LSTM去掉解码器，直接拿三个时间步最后一层的隐藏层接入MST，然后拿一个CNN预测头出结果，该方式是目前不加入SPHERE表现最好的，但是SPHERE对该模型无提升","x":480,"y":1618,"width":265,"height":182,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"6e553c2c1d7da387","type":"text","text":"ConvLSTM_MSTRefiner_Raw_seed11 RMSE: 0.9016","x":129,"y":1660,"width":250,"height":69,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"3b8c42ca526bedb4","type":"text","text":"再加上SPHERE","x":17,"y":1461,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"5ea537f27865c118","type":"text","text":"seed11 RMSE 0.8854","x":335,"y":1461,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"5daad0928e61330f","type":"text","text":"分解成季节背景场和动力异常残差，Convlstm_CARefiner  RMSE0.9463","x":878,"y":1333,"width":322,"height":70},
		{"id":"ae701a779e645b02","type":"text","text":"把SimVP并联到ConvLSTM 非常成功","x":11,"y":1284,"width":250,"height":60},
